st =\n|Northwest = [[Zhangjiakou]], Hebei\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Articles related to Beijing\n|list =\n{{Province-level divisions of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{Metropolitan cities of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{Most populous cities in the People's Republic of China}}\n{{List of Asian capitals by region}}\n{{Museums in Beijing}}\n{{Olympic Summer Games Host Cities}}\n{{Paralympic Summer Games Host Cities}}\n{{Olympic Winter Games Host Cities}}\n{{Paralympic Winter Games Host Cities}}\n{{Asian Games Host Cities}}\n{{IAAF World Championships in Athletics Host cities}}\n{{World's most populated urban areas}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Beijing| ]]<!--please leave the empty space as standard-->\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Capitals in Asia]]\n[[Category:Metropolitan areas of China]]\n[[Category:North China Plain]]\n", "text_old": "{{redirect|Peking|other uses|Beijing (disambiguation)|and|Peking (disambiguation)}}\n{{redirect|Beijinger|the magazine|the Beijinger}}\n\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n\n{{short description|Capital of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                = {{raise|0.2em|Beijing}}\n|native_name         = {{lower|0.1em|{{nobold|{{lang|zh|\u5317\u4eac\u5e02}}}}}}\n|other_name = Peking\n|settlement_type     = [[Direct-administered municipalities of China|Municipality]]\n|image_skyline       = {{multiple image\n| border                 = infobox\n| total_width            = 280\n| image_style            = border:1;\n| perrow                 = 1/2/2/1\n| image1                 = Beijing Skyline.webp\n| image2                 = Tiananmen Gate.jpg\n| image3                 = The Great Wall of China - Badaling.jpg\n| image4                 = Beijing National Stadium 1.jpg\n| image5                 = SA Temple of Heaven.jpg\n| image6                 = National Centre for the Performing Arts and Great Hall of the People.jpg\n}}\n|image_size         